File:Rokuon-jinja, honden.jpg|Main hall (Honden)
File:Rokuon-jinja, keidaisha.jpg|Shrine within the grounds
File:Rokuon-jinja, entrance.jpg|Torii at the entrance
File:Rokuon-jinja, torii.jpg|Additional torii
</gallery>

== Access ==

* A 10-minute walk from [[Iwata Station]] on the {{ill|Tōkaidō Main Line|ja|東海道本線|12=draft|12=draft}} operated by {{ill|JR Central|ja|東海旅客鉄道|12=draft|12=draft}}.

